2.00	Hastings_New_Zealand	Hastings, New Zealand	The city of Hastings is a major urban settlement in the Hawke's Bay region of the North Island of New Zealand, and it is the largest settlement by population in Hawke's Bay. Hastings city is the administrative centre of the Hastings District. Hastings is located some 20 km inland from the neighbouring port city of Napier.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/0/09/Hastings_District_from_Peak.jpg/300px-Hastings_District_from_Peak.jpg
